title: Lynlake Mansion- 3 Bedroom 1 Bath or 2 Bedroom and 1 Office, September

+ email + best time to call and a little about yourself, can also send you a video tour prior to a showing)', '***SHOWINGS: BY Appointment on Thursday evenings and Saturday (sometimes Sunday Afternoons', '...', '**YOU- Take into consideration via Individual Assesment- credit score (if affects ability to pay rent), criminal record, rental record- paid on time/not creating damage, #
